snippet.title: RBI Unexpectedly Keeps Rates Unchanged Despite Cash Crunch

localized.description:
The Reserve Bank of India (RBI) has kept its repo rate unchanged at 6.25 per cent in its first monetary policy review after the notes ban, surprising the street.
